Notice # 01-26

January 22, 2001


TO:  NYMEX/COMEX Division Members


FROM: George Henderson, Vice President


RE:  EOR Demonstration Schedule


Please be advised that the Human Factors Lab located on the 2nd floor,

opposite the Concierge Office, will be open each day to conduct

demonstrations of the Automated Trading Card (ATC) portion of the Electronic

Order Routing (EOR) system.


The HF Lab will be available Monday through Friday, from 11:00 a.m. to 5:00

p.m.  All demonstrations of the system will be conducted by appointment

only.  To schedule a hand held demo call the Floor Department Systems Area at

299-2626.


During these demos your comments and suggestions will be documented and

reviewed for possible future system modifications and enhancements.


